  "detailed_description": "<h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 extra themes </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Downloadable Wallpapers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music player </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 more collection room</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time to find ALL the stuff!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/2dc294ced3ea441ea8485aefce9959da.poster.avif?t=1729511412\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/2dc294ced3ea441ea8485aefce9959da.webm?t=1729511412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/2dc294ced3ea441ea8485aefce9959da.mp4?t=1729511412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this hidden object game, you will go through beautifully arranged themed levels and clear out different scenes. Enjoy playing a variety of mini-games while collecting little trinkets to fill a room with! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/c012403583f6357a53afd9a560172799.poster.avif?t=1729511412\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/c012403583f6357a53afd9a560172799.webm?t=1729511412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/c012403583f6357a53afd9a560172799.mp4?t=1729511412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So sit back, relax, and sort through so much stuff!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time to find ALL the stuff!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/2dc294ced3ea441ea8485aefce9959da.poster.avif?t=1729511412\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/2dc294ced3ea441ea8485aefce9959da.webm?t=1729511412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/2dc294ced3ea441ea8485aefce9959da.mp4?t=1729511412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this hidden object game, you will go through beautifully arranged themed levels and clear out different scenes. Enjoy playing a variety of mini-games while collecting little trinkets to fill a room with! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/c012403583f6357a53afd9a560172799.poster.avif?t=1729511412\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/c012403583f6357a53afd9a560172799.webm?t=1729511412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164100/extras/c012403583f6357a53afd9a560172799.mp4?t=1729511412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So sit back, relax, and sort through so much stuff!</p>",
